<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="68d5b4f2-1c8c-4fb4-bca0-ff21c03bc6c5"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="268c3a17-3198-43f5-aa28-e6e27cc364d8">Damage Resistances</span>&nbsp;bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing from nonmagical attacks</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="71cb8cb8-abaf-4d76-af81-0346fa998ec1"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="b50f79c7-acb7-4a05-9ee6-9b254c0ffb29">Damage Immunit</span><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="7e2f2483-f9e0-4ba5-83a9-a4e9a8f6f4d3">ies</span>&nbsp;poison</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="c2bb27c3-5bf5-4e6d-b244-eef54b38d1f5"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="7f330d46-d707-4c30-ba8a-21e88c5d1bf7">Condition Immunities</span>&nbsp;<a class="tooltip-hover condition-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Exhaustion" data-tooltip-href="/conditions/4-tooltip">exhaustion</a>, <a class="tooltip-hover condition-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Grappled" data-tooltip-href="/conditions/6-tooltip">grappled</a>, <a class="tooltip-hover condition-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Paralyzed" data-tooltip-href="/conditions/9-tooltip">paralyzed</a>, <a class="tooltip-hover condition-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Petrified" data-tooltip-href="/conditions/10-tooltip">petrified</a>, <a class="tooltip-hover condition-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Poisoned" data-tooltip-href="/conditions/11-tooltip">poisoned</a>, <a class="tooltip-hover condition-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Prone" data-tooltip-href="/conditions/12-tooltip">prone</a>, <a class="tooltip-hover condition-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Restrained" data-tooltip-href="/conditions/13-tooltip">restrained</a>, <a class="tooltip-hover condition-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Unconscious" data-tooltip-href="/conditions/15-tooltip">unconscious</a></p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="6a8ebfb2-07f1-445e-a565-51a400993fb7"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="1e5c43c1-c9c6-40ba-b0e4-a1b6ae5dd3fe">Senses</span>&nbsp;<a class="tooltip-hover sense-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/monsters#Darkvision" data-tooltip-href="/senses/2-tooltip">darkvision</a> 60 ft., passive Perception 18</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="f8642191-88a5-4af3-9422-bc31f6897ac6"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="6d7d10c6-7070-413d-a7b9-c5af6d3a7941">Languages</span>&nbsp;Auran, understands Common but doesn’t speak it</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data-Last" data-content-chunk-id="a7c455bc-8ef9-4ddb-a69a-b45049c73142"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="008f2506-deba-41c7-8562-e0ed6da7b2f6">Challenge</span>&nbsp;6 (2,300 XP)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="8cb4a788-5a73-4a50-b647-67bdb2f720b6"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="642f434c-58ad-4977-94c0-c5b65955af0a">Invisibility.</span>&nbsp;The stalker is <a class="tooltip-hover condition-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Invisible" data-tooltip-href="/conditions/8-tooltip">invisible</a>.</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body-Last--apply-before-heading-" data-content-chunk-id="bd58c4d9-7237-4e81-8428-d575c84b696a"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="1b399c4c-0db5-4af6-b648-586799b21c26">Faultless Tracker.</span>&nbsp;The stalker is given a quarry by its summoner. The stalker knows the direction and distance to its quarry as long as the two of them are on the same plane of existence. The stalker also knows the location of its summoner.</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Heading" data-content-chunk-id="9258d033-1358-4616-be61-38e2ecee774d">Actions</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="2523ea56-034c-4aad-ac9c-4dbaf66bf813"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="a982c49d-a7ad-4390-9241-457205058247">Multiattack.&nbsp;</span>The stalker makes two slam attacks.</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="66d46601-fa7d-4563-8099-1ec871197d30"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="976e76f5-06e2-425a-a7b4-7f34a3e06dee">Slam.</span><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="e70ff7bc-5a2b-4f5d-af5d-2046ec04a40c">&nbsp;Melee Weapon Attack:</span>&nbsp;+6 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target.&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="fa4962af-ee29-4689-8441-799db8c7b755">Hit:</span>&nbsp;10 (2d6 + 3) bludgeoning damage.</p>
